It is with a heavy heart that we, the UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens Administrative and Moderating team, announce the end of our sixty-seven year sponsorship with Sizzler™ (Now you're talking). It was not an easy decision and we hope that Sizzler™ (Now you're talking) gets their shit together and stops being a fucking dickwad. Your Truly,
